Description: ou bet! This is the reincarnation and modern evolution of the famed honky-tonk, cowboy (and cowgirl) saloon and dance hall from Texas.Gilley_s Bar-B-Que retaurant is open for lunch and dinner featuring a show kitchen, views of the world-famous Las Vegas Strip, custom saddle seats at the bar, live entertainment, line dancing, mechanical bull riding, and of course, the world-famous Gilley Girls.
Location: 3300 S Las Vegas Blvd, Las Vegas, NV 89109
